casebody.data:
MBNA AMERICA BANK, N.A. Smith, Debnam, Narron, Wyche, Saintsing & Myers, L.L.P.
v.
Rodney FUNDERBURK. No. 180P08. Supreme Court of North Carolina. June 11, 2008. Rodney Funderburk, Pro Se. Amanda Banat, for MBNA, et al.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 15th day of April 2008 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the decision of the North Carolina Court of Appeals, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 11th day of June 2008."
